window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In Harrow's eerie tale of madness and heartache, Patience, diagnosed with a \"nervous disposition,\" is forced to take up residence in the rural, dilapidated Gravely House, in hopes that she will \"calm down and get better\" before her senior year begins. But when she discovers a girl living inside her bedroom mirror, the past comes back to haunt, in more ways than one. </p>"; 
